      "response": "Here is your concise technical orientation for the **WORKMAT** project.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"primary_language\": \"TypeScript\",\n  \"entry_points\": [\n    \"src/app/api/chat/route.ts (POST/GET/DELETE/PATCH) — multi-provider chat hub (Vapi, local LLM, OpenAI); orchestrates conversation logic, lead extraction, and session lifecycle\",\n    \"src/app/api/vapi_chat/route.ts — Vapi-specific chat integration connector\",\n    \"src/app/api/admin/analytics/overview/route.ts — analytics GET endpoint; aggregates visits, leads, chats, sources and time-series data (development + production via SSH)\",\n    \"src/lib/maintenance/index.ts — server maintenance library (disk usage, catalog cleanup, pgBackRest expire)\",\n    \"src/app/admin/mailing/page.tsx — Admin mailing campaign manager (4519-line god component: templates, audiences, A/B testing, sending)\",\n    \"src/components/chat/ChatWidget.tsx — main chat React UI widget (2993 lines, handles local/OpenAI/Vapi providers)\",\n    \"src/components/call/CallWidget.tsx — voice/video call React UI widget (2262 lines)\"\n  ],\n  \"hotspots\": [\n    \"app.api.admin.analytics.overview.route.map — 309 inbound deps (analytics aggregation logic, massive blast radius)\",\n    \"components.ConsoleNoiseFilter.useEffect — 275 inbound deps (audio filtering hook, UI coupling)\",\n    \"components.ContactForm.test — 249 inbound deps (contact form component)\",\n    \"app.api.vapi_chat.route.Number — 194 inbound deps (Vapi chat route helper)\",\n    \"lib.chatActionAuth.Boolean — 166 inbound deps (chat action authorization, complexity: 23)\",\n    \"lib.backups.toRecord — 134 inbound deps (backup record serialization)\",\n    \"components.call.CallWidget.t — 117 inbound deps (translation lookup in CallWidget)\",\n    \"app.admin.mailing.page.error — 112 inbound deps (mailing page error state)\",\n    \"lib.companyProfile.readString — 110 inbound deps (company profile reads)\",\n    \"app.admin.mailing.page.filter — 110 inbound deps (mailing page filtering logic)\"\n  ],\n  \"relevant_tests\": [\n    \"No test files found. The project declares tsx --test tests/**/*.test.ts in package.json scripts and includes Playwright as a devDependency, but no .test.ts or __tests__ directories exist in the indexed codebase.\"\n  ],\n  \"summary\": \"WORKMAT (workmat-web) is a Next.js 15 + React 19 + Prisma/PostgreSQL multi-tenant web application for managing agent communication (chat, voice calls, email marketing). It uses an event-driven architecture with three chat provider backends (Vapi AI, local LLM, OpenAI), an admin panel with analytics, user/TOTP MFA management, mailing campaign orchestration, and server maintenance tooling. The most critical risk areas are the analytics overview route (309 deps), chat authorization logic (complexity 23), and several god components (mailing page at 4519 lines, admin backups at 4381 lines, ChatWidget at 2993 lines). No test files currently exist despite Playwright and Node test runner being available. Changes to the analytics overview, chat routes, or admin mailing page have the highest blast radius and demand thorough regression testing.\"\n}\n```",
